This is a map of a house i used to live in! The map is close to scale with a few additions to the map...
This map is equip for plant_bomb style games or generally fight yard or gun game. Typically a small map but adds a bit of fun as a house style environment. If you would ever like to see the original house its located in Queensland , AUS.... Have fun! .. PS:In future I plan to put a picture of the house in the map!
